<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201210/da134182141f4cafb36e4317c7a5e175.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>动作3、空中单车</p>
<p>动作坚持10-15次，重复2组。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201210/9fb18914620d432a93d5a2559b559438.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
